{"tid":1667851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[we connect] Free Hug 南亞手足","createTime":"2019-10-21T16:28:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T00:52:30.000Z","uid":8217,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f431b69817aec5f99b85991b2f8c6af069467fe3","tid":1667851,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:28:40.000Z","msg":"見左好多訪問，發現啲南亞人話之前啲香港人好似唔鐘意同佢地有接觸，唔想掂到佢哋。搭地鐵又會行過啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢哋一直都覺得好唔開心。佢哋係真香港人嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以之前有人話會塞爆重慶大廈，食哂佢哋啲咖哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不如都喺門口搞個Free Hug，同佢哋多啲connection，又可以影多啲相方上Twitter等國際文宣平台<br />\n<br />\n召喚所有和理非！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999 好少出post"},{"pid":"4a6be0de39db82952e6c3f1accc5462a71027133","tid":1667851,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:28:55.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"ce00fafb4b3de4e7f8a986b25a7afc04b764cd6c","tid":1667851,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:29:05.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"80c16e9d46d89246b0631fbe5c2c182c379cd9a0","tid":1667851,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:29:16.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"8dd6696749007748ecba07d936696dbeaa1c69dc","tid":1667851,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"自推7"},{"pid":"9a94530e70f3427dcd18cfed163dcdf9fc9a9310","tid":1667851,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:29:38.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"93613ec121da44ea256003ec616475e23ce50698","tid":1667851,"uid":8217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"8